T1  - Is cash negative debt? A hedging perspective on corporate financial policies
AU  - Acharya, Viral V.
AU  - Almeida, Heitor
AU  - Campello, Murillo
JO  - Journal of Financial Intermediation
VL  - 16
IS  - 4
SP  - 515
